name: Amazing Princess Gymnastics Trampoline
description:
Join Amazing Princess to do awesome flips and tricks on trampoline! If you are a big fan of amazing princess gymnastics games, this is a must-have!
Do you have what it takes to become the gymnastics trampoline champion, showing off your back and front flips on trampoline? It is time to challenge yourself !

Bounce in the trampoline and don’t forget to not jump up into the balls to get the best high score among your friends. Beat their highscores by being the best at flipping in the air. You will never be bored again while you play this super fun gymnastics trampoline game.

Download and compete with all the Amazing Princess gymnastics lovers !
